---
// index.astro - Landing Page Profesional para Venta de Servicios Web
---
<html lang="es">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>Diseño de Páginas Web Profesionales | Tu Negocio en Internet</title>
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
		<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
		
		<style>
			body { 
				font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; 
				background-color: #0B1528; 
				color: #FFFFFF;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 0;
				min-height: 100vh;
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
			}
			.main-container {
				width: 100%;
				max-width: 440px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 40px 20px;
				box-sizing: border-box;
				display: flex;
				flex-direction: column;
				align-items: center;
			}
			.header-section {
				text-align: center;
				margin-bottom: 30px;
			}
			.main-title {
				font-size: 26px;
				font-weight: 700;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				color: #FFFFFF;
				margin: 0 0 8px 0;
				letter-spacing: 1px;
			}
			.highlight-yellow {
				color: #FFD43F; 
				font-size: 14px;
				font-weight: 600;
				display: block;
				margin-top: 5px;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				letter-spacing: 2px;
			}
			.service-card {
				width: 100%;
				background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
				border-radius: 16px;
				padding: 20px;
				box-sizing: border-box;
				margin-bottom: 20px;
				text-align: left;
			}
			.border-blue { border: 1.5px solid #00C2FF; }
			.border-pink { border: 1.5px solid #FF007A; }
			.border-gold { border: 1.5px solid #FFD43F; }

			.card-header {
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				gap: 14px;
				margin-bottom: 10px;
			}
			.card-icon { font-size: 24px; }
			.card-title {
				font-size: 16px;
				font-weight: 700;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				margin: 0;
			}
			.card-description {
				font-size: 13px;
				color: #A0AEC0;
				line-height: 1.5;
				margin: 0;
			}
			.badge-recommended {
				background: #FF0055;
				color: #FFFFFF;
				font-size: 10px;
				font-weight: 700;
				padding: 4px 8px;
				border-radius: 6px;
				text-transform: uppercase;
			}
			.form-section {
				width: 100%;
				background: #122038;
				border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
				border-radius: 20px;
				padding: 24px;
				box-sizing: border-box;
				margin-top: 20px;
				text-align: center;
			}
			.form-title {
				font-size: 18px;
				font-weight: 700;
				color: #FFD43F;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				margin: 0 0 6px 0;
			}
			.form-subtitle {
				font-size: 12px;
				margin: 0 0 20px 0;
			}
			.form-group { margin-bottom: 14px; }
			.form-input {
				width: 100%;
				padding: 14px 16px;
				box-sizing: border-box;
				background: #0B1528;
				border: 1.5px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
				border-radius: 10px;
				font-size: 13px;
				color: #FFFFFF;
				outline: none;
			}
			.btn-submit {
				width: 100%;
				padding: 14px;
				background: #00E676; 
				color: #0B1528;
				border: none;
				border-radius: 10px;
				font-size: 14px;
				font-weight: 700;
				text-transform: uppercase;
				cursor: pointer;
			}
			.footer-section {
				width: 100%;
				text-align: center;
				margin-top: 30px;
			}
			.wa-link {
				color: #00E676;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 600;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	
	<body>
		<main class="main-container">
			<div class="header-section">
				<h1 class="main-title">¿Tu Negocio</h1>
				<span class="highlight-yellow">¿Aún no vendes en internet?</span>
			</div>

			<div class="service-card border-blue">
				<div class="card-header">
					<span class="card-icon">💻</span>
					<h2 class="card-title">Página Web Informativa</h2>
				</div>
				<p class="card-description">Ideal para darte a conocer. Incluye diseño moderno, adaptado a celulares y presencia en Google.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="service-card border-pink">
				<div class="card-header">
					<span class="card-icon">🛒</span>
					<h2 class="card-title">Tienda en Línea Completa</h2>
				</div>
				<p class="card-description">Sube tus productos, recibe pagos con tarjeta y administra tus ventas de forma automática.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="service-card border-gold">
				<div class="card-header">
					<span class="card-icon">🎓</span>
					<h2 class="card-title">Te la diseñamos + Curso</h2>
					<span class="badge-recommended">¡Recomendado!</span>
				</div>
				<p class="card-description">Creamos la estructura de tu web y te capacitamos de forma personalizada para que tú hagas el resto sin pagar mantenimiento.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="form-section">
				<h3 class="form-title">¿Quieres Cotizar o Agendar?</h3>
				<p class="form-subtitle">Escríbenos para enviarte nuestros paquetes y precios al instante.</p>
				<form action="#" method="POST">
					<div class="form-group"><input type="text" placeholder="Nombre completo" class="form-input" /></div>
					<div class="form-group"><input type="tel" placeholder="Número de WhatsApp" class="form-input" /></div>
					<button type="submit" class="btn-submit">Solicitar Información</button>
				</form>
			</div>

			<div class="footer-section">
				<a href="<a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=529981264934&text=Hola%20Elizabeth,%20vi%20tu%20p%C3%A1gina%20web%20y%20me%20gustar%C3%ADa%20cotizar%20un%20paquete" target="_blank" class="wa-link">🟢 WhatsApp: 998 126 4934</a>">
			</div>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>
